WEBVTT

03:26.040 --> 03:29.480
The Missile of the Isle of Man,
Mark Cavendish.

04:31.160 --> 04:35.160
Here is one of
the superstar international sprinters,

04:35.240 --> 04:39.440
Mark Cavendish!

10:19.880 --> 10:25.160
It's Mark Cavendish
putting the yellow jersey on.

10:34.400 --> 10:36.160
Look how happy he is.

10:36.240 --> 10:37.680
He's never worn this jersey,

10:37.760 --> 10:39.200
and he's wearing it today.

28:16.200 --> 28:17.640
Close the gap!

28:19.440 --> 28:21.040
What the fuck is he doing?

01:24:57.840 --> 01:24:59.680
We made history!

01:30:18.280 --> 01:30:22.400
Good morning from Austria
with Bernie Eisel.
